{"tid":322281,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一有抑鬱症好似好難好返......","createTime":"2017-07-14T16:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-15T16:14:50.000Z","uid":81387,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d7fed78293303f7b442c3d41c39d1c28e938d91","tid":322281,"uid":81387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:32:15.000Z","msg":"阿媽因為阿爸身體唔好搞到有抑鬱症，我又大壓力，已經一年起崩潰邊緣日日喊同冇乜野之間浮沉，覺得所有野返唔到去未有事之前咁......<br />\n<br />\n我有去見輔導，但始終解決唔到現存問題係冇辦法變好。阿媽阿爸情況唔好，我成個情緒都壞左，好難覺得開心，成日精神都唔振奮，返工冇力扮smart扮有熱誠......用一種好辛苦既狀態繼續做緊人形物，唔知可以點樣令自己好返d......<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a12617678af275b41026e9152382487ee495ff","tid":322281,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:32:31.000Z","msg":"要有自信"},{"pid":"5d4395af8b9965cb175555778df95fff0a260d30","tid":322281,"uid":81387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:36:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要有自信</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bd690bea34d48a97722f2119a2b03581425cf2","tid":322281,"uid":19095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:43:34.000Z","msg":"搵樹窿"},{"pid":"bafab5d191648c078615aa56d2a5c94760831eb9","tid":322281,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"揾個男朋友"},{"pid":"0f90b754c01d94e137f5d20bf8aca6d00eeff092","tid":322281,"uid":81387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揾個男朋友</blockquote><br />\n我會係，覺得自己都處理唔好，攞唔到其他精力出黎拍拖......"},{"pid":"2ff2e1230af42f6d1d39ed3f414af362e8450355","tid":322281,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>揾個男朋友</blockquote><br />\n我會係，覺得自己都處理唔好，攞唔到其他精力出黎拍拖......</blockquote><br />\n揾個愛你嘅人攬住自己 已經可以放低好多野"},{"pid":"0